00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:21,740
 I like a lot about it, but I do like my curly braces

201
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,420
 because for me, I like to see the beginning and end of blocks,

202
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:27,020
 whereas in Python, you only see the beginning,

203
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:28,220
 but that's okay.

204
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:30,540
 I'm just saying that now you're going to see

